<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>NFCKartify — Kurumsal Dijital Kartvizit</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --bg:   #1c1c20;
      --bg2:  #222227;
      --bg3:  #28282e;
      --bg4:  #2e2e35;
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      --border-gold: rgba(200,168,75,0.35);
      --gold: #c8a84b;
      --gold-light: #e5c46a;
      --gold-dim: rgba(200,168,75,0.12);
      --text: #f0eeea;
      --text-muted: #8a8880;
      --text-faint: #484844;
      --fs-xs: 0.72rem;
      --fs-sm: 0.8rem;
      --fs-base: 0.875rem;
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.5; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; overflow-x: hidden; }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      height: 56px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 32px;
      background: rgba(28,28,32,0.88); backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .logo { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .logo em { font-style: normal; color: var(--gold); }
    .nav-right { display: flex; gap: 8px; }
    .btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 32px; padding: 0 14px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: var(--fs-sm); font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; border: none; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.15s; white-space: nowrap; }
    .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--text-muted); }
    .btn-ghost:hover { background: var(--bg3); color: var(--text); }
    .btn-gold { background: var(--gold); color: #000; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(200,168,75,0.25); }
    .btn-gold:hover { background: var(--gold-light); box-shadow: 0 0 32px rgba(200,168,75,0.4); }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero { padding: 112px 32px 80px; text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; }
    .hero-glow { position: fixed; top: -100px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 700px; height: 500px; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(200,168,75,0.07) 0%, transparent 65%); pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; }
    .hero > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

    .live-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; padding: 5px 13px; background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 100px; font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 24px; animation: fadeUp 0.6s both; }
    .live-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: #22c55e; border-radius: 50%; box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(34,197,94,0.7); animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
    @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{box-shadow:0 0 6px rgba(34,197,94,0.6)} 50%{box-shadow:0 0 14px rgba(34,197,94,1)} }
    @keyframes fadeUp { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)} to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)} }
    @keyframes shimmer { from{background-position:200% 0} to{background-position:-200% 0} }

    h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.25rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.04em; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 18px; animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s both; }
    .gold-text { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c8a84b 0%, #f0d878 45%, #c8a84b 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; background-size: 200%; animation: shimmer 5s linear infinite; }
    .hero-desc { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 28px; animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.2s both; }
    .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 56px; animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.3s both; }
    .btn-hero { height: 42px; padding: 0 20px; font-size: var(--fs-sm); border-radius: 8px; }
    .btn-outline-hero { height: 42px; padding: 0 20px; font-size: var(--fs-sm); border-radius: 8px; background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: none; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; font-weight: 500; font-family: inherit; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; }
    .btn-outline-hero:hover { border-color: var(--border-gold); color: var(--text); }

    /* ── NFC CARDS ── */
    .cards-scene { display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: flex-end; animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.4s both; }
    .card-wrap { cursor: pointer; }
    .card-wrap:nth-child(1) { transform: rotate(-5deg) translateY(10px); z-index: 1; }
    .card-wrap:nth-child(2) { z-index: 3; margin: 0 -12px; }
    .card-wrap:nth-child(3) { transform: rotate(5deg) translateY(10px); z-index: 1; }
    .nfc-card { width: 200px; height: 126px; border-radius: 12px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: box-shadow 0.3s; }
    .card-wrap:nth-child(2) .nfc-card { width: 224px; height: 142px; }
    .card-black { background: linear-gradient(145deg,#1c1c1c,#2a2a2a,#111); box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
    .card-gold-card { background: linear-gradient(145deg,#8a6820,#c8a84b,#e8c860,#c0952a,#a07818); box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(200,168,75,0.4); }
    .card-white-card { background: linear-gradient(145deg,#e8e8e8,#f2f2f2,#e0e0e0); box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
    .card-chip { position: absolute; top: 12px; left: 13px; width: 30px; height: 22px; border-radius: 4px; }
    .card-black .card-chip { background: linear-gradient(135deg,#c8a84b,#f0d060); }
    .card-gold-card .card-chip { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.28); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.45); }
    .card-white-card .card-chip { background: linear-gradient(135deg,#a8a8a8,#d0d0d0); }
    .card-chip::before,.card-chip::after { content:''; position:absolute; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
    .card-chip::before { top:7px; left:3px; right:3px; height:1px; }
    .card-chip::after { top:3px; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%); width:1px; height:calc(100% - 6px); }
    .card-nfc { position: absolute; top: 12px; right: 12px; width: 20px; height: 20px; opacity: 0.45; }
    .card-black .card-nfc,.card-gold-card .card-nfc { color: #fff; }
    .card-white-card .card-nfc { color: #222; }
    .card-nfc-ring { position: absolute; top: 8px; right: 8px; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; border: 1px solid currentColor; opacity: 0; animation: nfcRing 2.5s ease-out infinite; }
    .card-black .card-nfc-ring { color: rgba(200,168,75,0.6); }
    .card-gold-card .card-nfc-ring { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); animation-delay: 0.9s; }
    .card-white-card .card-nfc-ring { color: rgba(0,0,0,0.25); animation-delay: 1.8s; }
    @keyframes nfcRing { 0%{opacity:.8;transform:scale(.6)} 100%{opacity:0;transform:scale(1.9)} }
    .card-footer { position: absolute; bottom:0; left:0; right:0; padding: 7px 13px; }
    .card-name { font-size: 0.52rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.07em; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .card-role { font-size: 0.44rem; margin-top: 1px; }
    .card-black .card-name { color: rgba(255,255,255,.88); } .card-black .card-role { color: rgba(255,255,255,.35); }
    .card-gold-card .card-name { color: rgba(255,255,255,.95); } .card-gold-card .card-role { color: rgba(255,255,255,.6); }
    .card-white-card .card-name { color: rgba(0,0,0,.7); } .card-white-card .card-role { color: rgba(0,0,0,.35); }
    .card-sheen { position:absolute; top:0; left:-100%; width:50%; height:100%; background:linear-gradient(105deg,transparent 40%,rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 50%,transparent 60%); transform:skewX(-8deg); pointer-events:none; }

    /* 3D tilt — handled via JS */
    .nfc-card { transform-style: preserve-3d; }

    /* ── DIVIDER ── */
    .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }

    /* ── STATS ── */
    .stats { display: flex; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .stat { flex:1; padding: 28px 24px; text-align: center; border-right: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .stat:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .stat-n { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: -0.05em; }
    .stat-l { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: var(--text-faint); margin-top: 3px; }

    /* ═══════════════════════════════════════
       BENTO FEATURES
    ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
    .bento-section { padding: 80px 32px; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .bento-label { font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .bento-title { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.04em; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 48px; line-height: 1.1; }

    .bento-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
      grid-template-rows: auto;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .bcard {
      background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; position: relative;
      transition: border-color 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s;
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
      transition: opacity 0.5s, transform 0.5s, border-color 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s;
    }
    .bcard.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    .bcard:hover { border-color: var(--border-gold); box-shadow: 0 0 32px rgba(200,168,75,0.06); }

    /* Grid placement */
    .bc1 { grid-column: span 5; } /* Dijital Profil — geniş */
    .bc2 { grid-column: span 4; } /* NFC & QR */
    .bc3 { grid-column: span 3; } /* Analitik */
    .bc4 { grid-column: span 3; } /* Toplu Yükleme */
    .bc5 { grid-column: span 4; } /* E-posta İmzası */
    .bc6 { grid-column: span 5; } /* White-label */

    .bcard-body { padding: 24px; }
    .bcard-tag { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 600; color: var(--gold); background: var(--gold-dim); border: 1px solid var(--border-gold); border-radius: 100px; padding: 3px 10px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .bcard-title { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 6px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .bcard-desc { font-size: var(--fs-sm); color: var(--text-faint); line-height: 1.6; }

    /* Visual areas */
    .bcard-visual { position: relative; overflow: hidden; }

    /* ── BC1: Dijital Profil — mini phone ── */
    .bc1 .bcard-visual { height: 180px; background: linear-gradient(160deg, var(--bg3) 0%, var(--bg4) 100%); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .mini-phone { width: 100px; border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 18px; background: var(--bg2); padding: 8px; position: relative; box-shadow: 0 20px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.4); }
    .mini-notch { width: 30px; height: 4px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 2px; margin: 0 auto 10px; }
    .mini-avatar { width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), #a07818); margin: 0 auto 6px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: #000; }
    .mini-name { font-size: 0.45rem; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .mini-role { font-size: 0.38rem; text-align: center; color: var(--text-faint); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .mini-divider { height: 1px; background: var(--border); margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .mini-btn { height: 12px; border-radius: 3px; background: var(--bg3); border: 1px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .mini-btn:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    /* Float badge */
    .float-badge { position: absolute; background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 5px 8px; font-size: 0.5rem; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; white-space: nowrap; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
    .fb-dot { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; }
    .fb-green { background: #22c55e; box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(34,197,94,0.7); }
    .fb-gold { background: var(--gold); }

    /* ── BC2: NFC rings ── */
    .bc2 .bcard-visual { height: 140px; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, rgba(200,168,75,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .nfc-rings { position: relative; width: 80px; height: 80px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .nfc-ring-anim { position: absolute; border-radius: 50%; border: 1.5px solid var(--gold); opacity: 0; animation: ringOut 2.5s ease-out infinite; }
    .nfc-ring-anim:nth-child(1) { width: 30px; height: 30px; animation-delay: 0s; }
    .nfc-ring-anim:nth-child(2) { width: 52px; height: 52px; animation-delay: 0.5s; }
    .nfc-ring-anim:nth-child(3) { width: 74px; height: 74px; animation-delay: 1s; }
    @keyframes ringOut { 0%{opacity:.8;transform:scale(.5)} 100%{opacity:0;transform:scale(1)} }
    .nfc-center-icon { width: 28px; height: 28px; background: var(--gold); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; z-index: 1; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(200,168,75,0.5); }

    /* ── BC3: Mini bar chart ── */
    .bc3 .bcard-visual { height: 120px; padding: 16px 16px 0; display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 5px; }
    .bar { flex: 1; border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0; background: var(--bg3); transition: height 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.34,1.56,0.64,1); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .bar-fill { position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0; background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gold-light), var(--gold)); transition: height 1s cubic-bezier(0.34,1.56,0.64,1); }
    .bar.b1 { height: 60%; } .bar.b2 { height: 80%; } .bar.b3 { height: 45%; } .bar.b4 { height: 90%; } .bar.b5 { height: 65%; } .bar.b6 { height: 100%; }

    /* ── BC4: Excel rows ── */
    .bc4 .bcard-visual { padding: 16px 16px 0; }
    .excel-row { display: flex; gap: 4px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .excel-cell { flex:1; height: 18px; border-radius: 3px; background: var(--bg3); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .excel-cell.header { background: var(--gold-dim); border-color: var(--border-gold); }
    .excel-cell.filled { animation: fillIn 0.4s both; }
    @keyframes fillIn { from{background:var(--bg3);width:0} to{background:var(--bg3);width:100%} }

    /* ── BC5: Email sig ── */
    .bc5 .bcard-visual { padding: 16px; }
    .email-mock { background: var(--bg3); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; }
    .email-header { padding: 8px 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-faint); }
    .email-body { padding: 10px 12px; }
    .email-body-text { font-size: 0.45rem; color: var(--text-faint); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .email-sig { border-top: 2px solid var(--gold); padding-top: 8px; display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center; }
    .sig-avatar { width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%; background: linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold),#a07818); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .sig-info-name { font-size: 0.45rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
    .sig-info-role { font-size: 0.38rem; color: var(--text-faint); }
    .sig-info-links { display: flex; gap: 4px; margin-top: 3px; }
    .sig-link { font-size: 0.38rem; color: var(--gold); text-decoration: underline; }

    /* ── BC6: White-label ── */
    .bc6 .bcard-visual { height: 120px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 16px; padding: 16px; }
    .brand-pill { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 100px; border: 1px solid; font-size: 0.5rem; font-weight: 700; transition: all 0.3s; }
    .bp1 { background: rgba(37,99,235,0.15); border-color: rgba(37,99,235,0.3); color: #60a5fa; }
    .bp2 { background: rgba(200,168,75,0.15); border-color: var(--border-gold); color: var(--gold); }
    .bp3 { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.12); border-color: rgba(239,68,68,0.25); color: #f87171; }
    .bp-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; }
    .bp1 .bp-dot { background: #3b82f6; }
    .bp2 .bp-dot { background: var(--gold); }
    .bp3 .bp-dot { background: #ef4444; }

    /* ═══════════════════════════════════════
       PREMIUM PRICING
    ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
    .pricing-section { padding: 80px 32px; }
    .pricing-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 56px; }
    .pricing-header h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.04em; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .pricing-header p { font-size: var(--fs-sm); color: var(--text-faint); }

    .pricing-wrap { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }

    .price-card {
      border-radius: 20px; padding: 32px;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .price-card-standard {
      background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: border-color 0.25s;
    }
    .price-card-standard:hover { border-color: var(--border-gold); }

    .price-card-featured {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1e1a0c 0%, #261f0a 50%, #1a1608 100%);
      border: 1px solid var(--gold);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(200,168,75,0.15), 0 32px 80px rgba(200,168,75,0.12), inset 0 0 60px rgba(200,168,75,0.03);
    }

    /* Featured top glow */
    .price-card-featured::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; top: 0; left: 10%; right: 10%; height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
    }
    /* Corner sparkle */
    .price-card-featured::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; top: -60px; right: -60px;
      width: 200px; height: 200px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(200,168,75,0.12) 0%, transparent 65%);
    }

    .price-popular {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
      background: var(--gold); color: #000;
      font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 100px; margin-bottom: 20px;
      animation: glow 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes glow { 0%,100%{box-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(200,168,75,0.4)} 50%{box-shadow:0 0 24px rgba(200,168,75,0.8)} }
    .pop-dot { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: #000; }

    .price-plan-name { font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-faint); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .price-plan-name.gold-name { color: var(--gold); }

    .price-amount { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 4px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .price-num { font-size: 2.75rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.06em; color: #fff; line-height: 1; }
    .price-card-featured .price-num { color: var(--gold); }
    .price-per { font-size: var(--fs-sm); color: var(--text-faint); }
    .price-desc { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: var(--text-faint); margin-bottom: 28px; padding-bottom: 28px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); line-height: 1.6; }
    .price-card-featured .price-desc { border-bottom-color: rgba(200,168,75,0.15); }

    .price-feats { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .price-feats li { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; font-size: var(--fs-sm); }
    .pf-icon { width: 18px; height: 18px; border-radius: 5px; flex-shrink: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-top: 1px; }
    .pf-icon-check { background: var(--gold-dim); }
    .pf-icon-check svg { color: var(--gold); }
    .pf-icon-arrow { background: var(--bg3); }
    .pf-icon-arrow svg { color: var(--text-faint); }
    .pf-text { color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.4; }
    .price-card-featured .pf-text { color: var(--text); }

    .price-btn { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 6px; width: 100%; height: 46px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: var(--fs-sm); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit; transition: all 0.2s; }
    .price-btn-border { background: transparent; color: var(--text-muted); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .price-btn-border:hover { border-color: var(--border-gold); color: var(--text); }
    .price-btn-gold { background: var(--gold); color: #000; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(200,168,75,0.35); }
    .price-btn-gold:hover { background: var(--gold-light); box-shadow: 0 4px 32px rgba(200,168,75,0.55); transform: translateY(-1px); }

    /* ── CTA ── */
    .cta-wrap { padding: 0 32px 48px; }
    .cta {
      max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg2) 0%, #1a1508 50%, var(--bg2) 100%);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-gold); border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 56px 48px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .cta::before { content:''; position:absolute; top:-80px; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%); width:400px; height:300px; background:radial-gradient(ellipse,rgba(200,168,75,0.1) 0%,transparent 70%); pointer-events:none; }
    .cta > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .cta h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2rem); font-weight: 800; color: #fff; letter-spacing: -0.04em; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .cta p { font-size: var(--fs-sm); color: var(--text-faint); margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .cta-btns { display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

    /* ── TRUST ── */
    .trust { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:28px; padding:20px 32px; border-top:1px solid var(--border); flex-wrap:wrap; }
    .trust-item { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; font-size:var(--fs-xs); color:var(--text-faint); }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer { padding:18px 32px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; border-top:1px solid var(--border); flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; }
    .footer-logo { font-size:var(--fs-sm); font-weight:800; color:var(--text); text-decoration:none; }
    .footer-logo em { font-style:normal; color:var(--gold); }
    .footer-links { display:flex; gap:18px; }
    .footer-links a,.footer-links button { font-size:var(--fs-xs); color:var(--text-faint); text-decoration:none; background:none; border:none; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; transition:color 0.15s; }
    .footer-links a:hover,.footer-links button:hover { color:var(--text-muted); }
    .footer-copy { font-size:var(--fs-xs); color:var(--text-faint); }

    /* ── LOGIN MODAL ── */
    .modal-overlay { position:fixed; inset:0; z-index:200; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.75); backdrop-filter:blur(8px); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:16px; opacity:0; pointer-events:none; transition:opacity 0.2s; }
    .modal-overlay.open { opacity:1; pointer-events:all; }
    .modal { background:var(--bg2); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:18px; width:100%; max-width:380px; padding:32px; position:relative; transform:translateY(16px) scale(0.97); transition:transform 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1); box-shadow:0 40px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.6); }
    .modal-overlay.open .modal { transform:translateY(0) scale(1); }
    .modal::before { content:''; position:absolute; top:0; left:15%; right:15%; height:1px; background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--gold),transparent); }
    .modal-close { position:absolute; top:16px; right:16px; width:28px; height:28px; border-radius:6px; background:var(--bg3); border:1px solid var(--border); color:var(--text-muted); font-size:1rem; cursor:pointer; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; transition:all 0.15s; }
    .modal-close:hover { background:var(--border); color:var(--text); }
    .modal-logo { font-size:var(--fs-base); font-weight:800; color:var(--text); margin-bottom:4px; }
    .modal-logo em { font-style:normal; color:var(--gold); }
    .modal-sub { font-size:var(--fs-xs); color:var(--text-faint); margin-bottom:22px; }
    .modal-tabs { display:flex; background:var(--bg3); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:8px; padding:3px; margin-bottom:22px; }
    .modal-tab { flex:1; padding:6px; text-align:center; border-radius:6px; font-size:var(--fs-xs); font-weight:500; color:var(--text-muted); cursor:pointer; transition:all 0.15s; border:none; background:transparent; font-family:inherit; }
    .modal-tab.active { background:var(--bg2); color:var(--gold); box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.4); }
    .modal-form { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:11px; }
    .modal-form label { font-size:var(--fs-xs); color:var(--text-muted); display:block; margin-bottom:4px; }
    .modal-form input { width:100%; height:40px; padding:0 12px; background:var(--bg3); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:7px; color:var(--text); font-size:var(--fs-sm); font-family:inherit; outline:none; transition:border-color 0.15s,box-shadow 0.15s; }
    .modal-form input:focus { border-color:var(--gold); box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(200,168,75,0.1); }
    .modal-form input::placeholder { color:var(--text-faint); }
    .modal-submit { width:100%; height:42px; background:var(--gold); border:none; border-radius:8px; font-size:var(--fs-sm); font-weight:600; color:#000; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; transition:all 0.15s; box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(200,168,75,0.3); }
    .modal-submit:hover { background:var(--gold-light); box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(200,168,75,0.5); }
    .modal-flash-error { background:rgba(239,68,68,0.1); border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.2); color:#f87171; font-size:var(--fs-xs); padding:8px 12px; border-radius:6px; }
    .modal-divider { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; }
    .modal-divider::before,.modal-divider::after { content:''; flex:1; height:1px; background:var(--border); }
    .modal-divider span { font-size:var(--fs-xs); color:var(--text-faint); white-space:nowrap; }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .bento-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .bc1,.bc2,.bc3,.bc4,.bc5,.bc6 { grid-column: span 1; }
      .pricing-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 420px; margin: 0 auto; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      nav { padding: 0 16px; }
      .bento-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero { padding: 100px 16px 56px; }
      .cards-scene .card-wrap:nth-child(1),.cards-scene .card-wrap:nth-child(3) { display:none; }
      .stats { flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .stat { border-right:none!important; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); }
      .bento-section,.pricing-section,.cta-wrap { padding-left:16px; padding-right:16px; }
      footer { flex-direction:column; text-align:center; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero-glow"></div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a href="/" class="logo">NFC<em>Kartify</em></a>
  <div class="nav-right">
    <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="openModal('giris')">Giriş</button>
    <button class="btn btn-gold" onclick="openModal('kayit')">Başla →</button>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="live-badge"><span class="live-dot"></span>Şu an <span id="ticker" style="color:var(--gold);font-weight:600">142</span> kişi profil görüntülüyor</div>
  <h1>Çalışanlarınıza<br><span class="gold-text">dijital kimlik</span> verin</h1>
  <p class="hero-desc">Tek panelden tüm ekibi yönetin. NFC kart, QR kod ve link ile anında paylaşım. Her tıklamayı takip edin.</p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <button class="btn btn-gold btn-hero" onclick="openModal('kayit')">Ücretsiz Başla</button>
    <button class="btn-outline-hero" onclick="openModal('giris')">Giriş Yap</button>
  </div>

  <!-- CARDS -->
  <div class="cards-scene">
    <div class="card-wrap" id="cw0">
      <div class="nfc-card card-black">
        <div class="card-chip"></div>
        <svg class="card-nfc" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.5 12c0 4.69-3.81 8.5-8.5 8.5S3.5 16.69 3.5 12 7.31 3.5 12 3.5s8.5 3.81 8.5 8.5zM22 12C22 6.48 17.52 2 12 2S2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10zm-8 0c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2s-2-.9-2-2 .9-2 2-2 2 .9 2 2zm3 0c0 2.76-2.24 5-5 5s-5-2.24-5-5 2.24-5 5-5 5 2.24 5 5z"/></svg>
        <div class="card-nfc-ring"></div>
        <div class="card-footer"><div class="card-name">Ayşe Kaya</div><div class="card-role">Ürün Müdürü · Abdi İbrahim</div></div>
        <div class="card-sheen"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-wrap" id="cw1">
      <div class="nfc-card card-gold-card">
        <div class="card-chip"></div>
        <svg class="card-nfc" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.5 12c0 4.69-3.81 8.5-8.5 8.5S3.5 16.69 3.5 12 7.31 3.5 12 3.5s8.5 3.81 8.5 8.5zM22 12C22 6.48 17.52 2 12 2S2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10zm-8 0c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2s-2-.9-2-2 .9-2 2-2 2 .9 2 2zm3 0c0 2.76-2.24 5-5 5s-5-2.24-5-5 2.24-5 5-5 5 2.24 5 5z"/></svg>
        <div class="card-nfc-ring"></div>
        <div class="card-footer"><div class="card-name">Murat Özdemir</div><div class="card-role">Satış Temsilcisi · Pfizer</div></div>
        <div class="card-sheen"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-wrap" id="cw2">
      <div class="nfc-card card-white-card">
        <div class="card-chip"></div>
        <svg class="card-nfc" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.5 12c0 4.69-3.81 8.5-8.5 8.5S3.5 16.69 3.5 12 7.31 3.5 12 3.5s8.5 3.81 8.5 8.5zM22 12C22 6.48 17.52 2 12 2S2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10zm-8 0c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2s-2-.9-2-2 .9-2 2-2 2 .9 2 2zm3 0c0 2.76-2.24 5-5 5s-5-2.24-5-5 2.24-5 5-5 5 2.24 5 5z"/></svg>
        <div class="card-nfc-ring"></div>
        <div class="card-footer"><div class="card-name">Kerem Arslan</div><div class="card-role">Bölge Müdürü · MSD</div></div>
        <div class="card-sheen"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr class="divider">

<!-- STATS -->
<div class="stats">
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-n" data-target="500" data-suffix="+">0</div><div class="stat-l">Aktif profil</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-n" data-target="10" data-suffix="k+">0</div><div class="stat-l">Aylık görüntülenme</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-n" data-target="98" data-suffix="%">0</div><div class="stat-l">Memnuniyet</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-n">3 dk</div><div class="stat-l">Ortalama kurulum</div></div>
</div>

<!-- BENTO FEATURES -->
<div class="bento-section">
  <div class="bento-label">Özellikler</div>
  <div class="bento-title">Her şey tek platformda,<br><span class="gold-text">sıfır karmaşıklık</span></div>

  <div class="bento-grid">

    <!-- BC1: Dijital Profil -->
    <div class="bcard bc1">
      <div class="bcard-visual">
        <div style="position:relative;width:100%;height:180px;background:linear-gradient(160deg,var(--bg3),var(--bg4));display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;overflow:hidden;">
          <!-- BG circles -->
          <div style="position:absolute;width:200px;height:200px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(200,168,75,0.07),transparent 65%);top:-40px;right:-40px;"></div>
          <div class="mini-phone">
            <div class="mini-notch"></div>
            <div class="mini-avatar">MÖ</div>
            <div class="mini-name">Murat Özdemir</div>
            <div class="mini-role">Satış Temsilcisi · Pfizer</div>
            <div class="mini-divider"></div>
            <div class="mini-btn"></div>
            <div class="mini-btn"></div>
            <div class="mini-btn" style="width:60%;"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="float-badge" style="top:20px;right:20px;animation:floatB 4s ease-in-out infinite;">
            <span class="fb-dot fb-green"></span>
            <span style="color:var(--text-muted)">Profil görüntülendi</span>
          </div>
          <div class="float-badge" style="bottom:20px;left:20px;animation:floatB 4s ease-in-out infinite;animation-delay:-2s;">
            <span class="fb-dot fb-gold"></span>
            <span style="color:var(--text-muted)">Rehbere eklendi</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bcard-body">
        <div class="bcard-tag">📱 Dijital Profil</div>
        <div class="bcard-title">Her çalışana özel dijital kimlik</div>
        <div class="bcard-desc">Benzersiz URL, foto, telefon, e-posta, sosyal medya — hepsi tek sayfada. Ziyaretçi doğrudan rehbere ekleyebilir.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- BC2: NFC & QR -->
    <div class="bcard bc2">
      <div class="bcard-visual">
        <div style="height:140px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 60%,rgba(200,168,75,0.1),transparent 70%);">
          <div class="nfc-rings">
            <div class="nfc-ring-anim"></div>
            <div class="nfc-ring-anim"></div>
            <div class="nfc-ring-anim"></div>
            <div class="nfc-center-icon">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#000"><path d="M20.5 12c0 4.69-3.81 8.5-8.5 8.5S3.5 16.69 3.5 12 7.31 3.5 12 3.5s8.5 3.81 8.5 8.5zM22 12C22 6.48 17.52 2 12 2S2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10zm-8 0c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2s-2-.9-2-2 .9-2 2-2 2 .9 2 2zm3 0c0 2.76-2.24 5-5 5s-5-2.24-5-5 2.24-5 5-5 5 2.24 5 5z"/></svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bcard-body">
        <div class="bcard-tag">⚡ NFC &amp; QR</div>
        <div class="bcard-title">Tek dokunuş yeter</div>
        <div class="bcard-desc">NFC kart veya QR kod. Uygulama indirmeye gerek yok.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- BC3: Analitik -->
    <div class="bcard bc3">
      <div class="bcard-visual" style="padding:16px 16px 0;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:5px;height:100px;">
          <div class="bar b1"><div class="bar-fill" style="height:0" id="bar1"></div></div>
          <div class="bar b2"><div class="bar-fill" style="height:0" id="bar2"></div></div>
          <div class="bar b3"><div class="bar-fill" style="height:0" id="bar3"></div></div>
          <div class="bar b4"><div class="bar-fill" style="height:0" id="bar4"></div></div>
          <div class="bar b5"><div class="bar-fill" style="height:0" id="bar5"></div></div>
          <div class="bar b6"><div class="bar-fill" style="height:0" id="bar6"></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bcard-body">
        <div class="bcard-tag">📊 Analitik</div>
        <div class="bcard-title">Gerçek zamanlı</div>
        <div class="bcard-desc">Kim tıkladı, ne zaman, hangi link. Canlı veri.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- BC4: Toplu Yükleme -->
    <div class="bcard bc4">
      <div class="bcard-visual" style="padding:16px;">
        <div style="background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;">
          <div style="background:var(--gold-dim);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-gold);padding:5px 8px;display:flex;gap:4px;">
            <div style="width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:2px;background:var(--gold-dim);border:1px solid var(--border-gold);"></div>
            <div style="height:12px;flex:1;background:var(--gold-dim);border-radius:2px;border:1px solid var(--border-gold);"></div>
            <div style="height:12px;flex:1;background:var(--gold-dim);border-radius:2px;border:1px solid var(--border-gold);"></div>
          </div>
          <% for(let r=0;r<4;r++) { %>
          <div style="display:flex;gap:4px;padding:4px 8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
            <div style="width:12px;height:10px;border-radius:2px;background:var(--bg4);"></div>
            <div style="height:10px;flex:1;border-radius:2px;background:var(--bg4);"></div>
            <div style="height:10px;flex:1;border-radius:2px;background:var(--bg4);"></div>
          </div>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bcard-body">
        <div class="bcard-tag">📋 Toplu Yükleme</div>
        <div class="bcard-title">Excel'den sisteme</div>
        <div class="bcard-desc">100 çalışanı saniyeler içinde sisteme al.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- BC5: E-posta İmzası -->
    <div class="bcard bc5">
      <div class="bcard-visual" style="padding:14px;">
        <div class="email-mock">
          <div class="email-header">Kime: hekim@hastane.com.tr</div>
          <div class="email-body">
            <div class="email-body-text">Merhaba,<br>Bilgilendirme dökümanını ekte paylaşıyorum...</div>
            <div class="email-sig">
              <div class="sig-avatar"></div>
              <div>
                <div class="sig-info-name">Murat Özdemir</div>
                <div class="sig-info-role">Satış Temsilcisi · Pfizer Türkiye</div>
                <div class="sig-info-links">
                  <span class="sig-link">Profil</span>
                  <span class="sig-link">LinkedIn</span>
                  <span class="sig-link">Tel</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bcard-body">
        <div class="bcard-tag">✉️ E-posta İmzası</div>
        <div class="bcard-title">Otomatik HTML imzası</div>
        <div class="bcard-desc">Her profil için hazır imza. Kopyala, yapıştır. Kurumsal iletişim anında profesyonelleşir.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- BC6: White-label -->
    <div class="bcard bc6">
      <div class="bcard-visual" style="height:120px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:12px;padding:16px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--bg3),var(--bg4));">
        <div class="brand-pill bp1"><div class="bp-dot"></div>Abdi İbrahim</div>
        <div class="brand-pill bp2"><div class="bp-dot"></div>Pfizer TR</div>
        <div class="brand-pill bp3"><div class="bp-dot"></div>MSD</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bcard-body">
        <div class="bcard-tag">🏢 White-label</div>
        <div class="bcard-title">Marka kimliğinizle</div>
        <div class="bcard-desc">Logo, renk, özel alan adı. Bayi sistemi ile birden fazla firmayı tek yerden yönetin.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<!-- PRICING -->
<div class="pricing-section">
  <div class="pricing-header">
    <h2>Şeffaf fiyatlandırma</h2>
    <p>Gizli ücret yok. İstediğiniz zaman iptal.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pricing-wrap">

    <!-- BAYI -->
    <div class="price-card price-card-standard">
